#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.16:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Caravagga "
msgstr "2. Walking "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Sokhummasutta "
msgstr "16. Subtlety "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.18, sc1
msgctxt "an4.16:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, sokhummāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four kinds of subtlety. "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.16:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu rūpasokhummena samannāgato hoti paramena; "
msgstr "A mendicant has ultimate subtlety of form. "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.4"
msgid "tena ca rūpasokhummena aññaṃ rūpasokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na samanupassati; "
msgstr "They don’t see any other subtlety of form that’s better or finer than that, "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.5"
msgid "tena ca rūpasokhummena aññaṃ rūpasokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na pattheti. "
msgstr "nor do they aim for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.16:1.6"
msgid "Vedanāsokhummena samannāgato hoti paramena; "
msgstr "A mendicant has ultimate subtlety of feeling. "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.7"
msgid "tena ca vedanāsokhummena aññaṃ vedanāsokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na samanupassati; "
msgstr "They don’t see any other subtlety of feeling that’s better or finer than that, "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.8"
msgid "tena ca vedanāsokhummena aññaṃ vedanāsokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na pattheti. "
msgstr "nor do they aim for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.16:1.9"
msgid "Saññāsokhummena samannāgato hoti paramena; "
msgstr "A mendicant has ultimate subtlety of perception. "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.10"
msgid "tena ca saññāsokhummena aññaṃ saññāsokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na samanupassati; "
msgstr "They don’t see any other subtlety of perception that’s better or finer than that, "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.11"
msgid "tena ca saññāsokhummena aññaṃ saññāsokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na pattheti. "
msgstr "nor do they aim for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.16:1.12"
msgid "Saṅkhārasokhummena samannāgato hoti paramena; "
msgstr "A mendicant has ultimate subtlety of choices. "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.13"
msgid "tena ca saṅkhārasokhummena aññaṃ saṅkhārasokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na samanupassati; "
msgstr "They don’t see any other subtlety of choices that’s better or finer than that, "

msgctxt "an4.16:1.14"
msgid "tena ca saṅkhārasokhummena aññaṃ saṅkhārasokhummaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā na pattheti. "
msgstr "nor do they aim for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.16:1.15"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri sokhummānīti. "
msgstr "These are the four kinds of subtlety. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.16:2.1"
msgid "Rūpasokhummataṃ ñatvā, "
msgstr "Knowing the subtlety of form, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:2.2"
msgid "vedanānañca sambhavaṃ; "
msgstr "the cause of feelings, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:2.3"
msgid "Saññā yato samudeti, "
msgstr "where perception comes from, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:2.4"
msgid "atthaṃ gacchati yattha ca; "
msgstr "and where it ends; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:2.5"
msgid "Saṅkhāre parato ñatvā, "
msgstr "and knowing choices as other, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:2.6"
msgid "dukkhato no ca attato. "
msgstr "as suffering and not-self, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.16:3.1"
msgid "Sa ve sammaddaso bhikkhu, "
msgstr "that mendicant sees rightly, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:3.2"
msgid "santo santipade rato; "
msgstr "peaceful, in love with the state of peace. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:3.3"
msgid "Dhāreti antimaṃ dehaṃ, "
msgstr "They bear their final body, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.16:3.4"
msgid "jetvā māraṃ savāhinin”ti. "
msgstr "having vanquished Māra and his mount.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.16:3.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
